《'''瘋狂麥斯：憤怒道 原聲帶'''》（{{lang-en|''Mad Max: Fury Road Original Motion Picture Soundtrack''}}）是一套2015年美國末日後科幻[[動作片|動作片]]《[[瘋狂麥斯：憤怒道|瘋狂麥斯：憤怒道]]》的[[電影原聲帶|電影原聲帶]]，主要由[[Junkie_XL|Junkie XL]]作曲配樂。本原聲帶為[[水塔音樂|水塔音樂]]定於2015年5月12日發行<ref>{{cite web|last1=Jagernauth|first1=Kevin|title='Mad Max: Fury Road' Soundtrack Details Arrive, Listen To The First Pulse-Pounding Track|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/mad-max-fury-road-soundtrack-details-arrive-listen-to-the-first-pulse-pounding-track-20150401|website=[[Indiewire|Indiewire]]|publisher=[[SnagFilms|SnagFilms]]|accessdate=2015-04-08|date=2015-04-01|archive-date=2015-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403180301/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/mad-max-fury-road-soundtrack-details-arrive-listen-to-the-first-pulse-pounding-track-20150401|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而限量版的[[黑膠唱片|黑膠唱片]]版則於2015年7月發行<ref>{{cite web|title=Mad Max: Fury Road 2XLP|url=http://mondotees.com/products/mad-max-fury-road-original-motion-picture-soundtrack-2xlp|website=Mondo|accessdate=2015-05-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518221103/http://mondotees.com/products/mad-max-fury-road-original-motion-picture-soundtrack-2xlp|archivedate=2015-05-18}}</ref>。

==概要==
由於《[[瘋狂麥斯：憤怒道|瘋狂麥斯：憤怒道]]》經歷了一個漫長的製作時間，在此期間曾有數位作曲家有望為本片配樂，其中包括[[約翰·包威爾|約翰·包威爾]]和[[馬可·貝爾特拉米|馬可·貝爾特拉米]]<ref>{{cite web|last1=Goldwasser|first1=Dan|title=John Powell - Interview|url=http://www.soundtrack.net/content/article/?id=211|website=[[Soundtrack.Net|Soundtrack.Net]]|accessdate=2015-04-08|date=November 2006|archive-date=2015-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150415120048/http://www.soundtrack.net/content/article/?id=211|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=New Project: MAD MAX 4, Fans of Film Music audiopodcast|url=http://marco-beltrami.com/news2012.htm|website=The Marco Beltrami Universe|accessdate=2015-04-08|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141027052531/http://marco-beltrami.com/news2012.htm|archivedate=2014-10-27|date=2012-09-06}}</ref>。2013年10月，官方正式宣布[[Junkie_XL|Junkie XL]]將負責本片的配樂<ref>{{cite web|title=‘Mad Max: Fury Road’ to Feature Music by Junkie XL|url=http://filmmusicreporter.com/2013/10/16/mad-max-fury-road-to-feature-music-by-junkie-xl/|website=Film Music Reporter|accessdate=2015-04-08|date=2013-10-16|archive-date=2015-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150315062615/http://filmmusicreporter.com/2013/10/16/mad-max-fury-road-to-feature-music-by-junkie-xl/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。華納兄弟總裁副總裁戴倫·希格曼會見了他後，讓Junkie XL飛至[[悉尼|悉尼]]看了電影三小時左右的工作影像，同時也遇見了導演[[喬治·米勒|喬治·米勒]]<ref name="Collider1">{{cite web|last1=Weintraub|first1=Steve|title=Junkie XL Talks RUN ALL NIGHT, MAD MAX: FURY ROAD, BATMAN V SUPERMAN, and More|url=http://collider.com/junkie-xl-mad-max-fury-road-batman-v-superman-interview/|website=[[Collider.com|Collider.com]]|publisher=[[Complex_(magazine)|Complex]]|accessdate=2015-04-08|date=2015-03-11|archive-date=2015-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150407095427/http://collider.com/junkie-xl-mad-max-fury-road-batman-v-superman-interview/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由於米勒對於Junkie XL的之前為《[[300壯士：帝國崛起|300壯士：帝國崛起]]》配的樂和聽了他在現場對《瘋狂麥斯：憤怒道》的想法，因此決定讓他為本片作曲，並立即開始寫本電影的主題曲<ref name="Collider1" /><ref>{{cite web|last1=Roberts|first1=Sheila|title=Composer Junkie XL Talks 300: RISE OF AN EMPIRE, DIVERGENT, Possibly Collaborating with Hans Zimmer on INTERSTELLAR, MAD MAX: FURY ROAD, and More|url=http://collider.com/junkie-xl-mad-max-300-rise-of-empire-interview/|website=[[Collider.com|Collider.com]]|publisher=[[Complex_(magazine)|Complex]]|accessdate=2015-04-08|date=2014-03-18|archive-date=2015-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150425115532/http://collider.com/junkie-xl-mad-max-300-rise-of-empire-interview/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Junkie XL說：「我在2013年8月得到了此機會和我們（未完成）到2014年8月，當你這麼早開始玩，你將有很大的創作空間」<ref>{{cite web|last1=Burlingame|first1=Russ|title=Mad Max: Fury Road and Batman V Superman Composer Junkie XL Talks Scoring Blockbusters|url=http://comicbook.com/2015/04/07/q-a-mad-max-fury-road-and-batman-v-superman-composer-junkie-xl/|website=ComicBook.com|accessdate=2015-04-08|date=2015-04-07|archive-date=2015-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150410045921/http://comicbook.com/2015/04/07/q-a-mad-max-fury-road-and-batman-v-superman-composer-junkie-xl|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

